Winning numbers drawn in ‘Georgia FIVE Midday’ game
ATLANTA (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday afternoon’s drawing of the Georgia Lottery’s “Georgia FIVE Midday” game were:
7-1-0-0-2
(seven, one, zero, zero, two)
